{
  "$schema": "https://www.designtokens.org/schemas/2025.10/format.json",
  "$description": "boing-candy is HeiGe-Design's high-bounce candy system for consumer tools and lightweight SaaS. A cotton-pink canvas, a bubblegum primary that carries deep grape ink instead of timid white, and mint plus lemon accents stacked like a gumball dispenser. Fat rounded Baloo 2 display lands with squash-and-stretch spring; the gumdrop mascot Bibo peeks between the cards. One token set drives both the interface and the 16:9 deck, and nothing floats on the flat blur shadows that give AI slop away.",
